Loan_Questionnaire table stores Items, which are main questions, and sub-items inside each main question.

- loan_type_question: determines questions of which loan type 
- icon : specific question icons
- page_title : title of question
-condition_display_question: determines condition to display which answer set (depending on previous answer).
- is_hide_item: condition to display or hide special input
